The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                               IN THE CITY
                  
	 East Bengal have been clubbed with South African outfit Santos FC and Mahindra United in the IFA Shield. The other group has Mohun Bagan, Churchill Brothers, Pradyut Dutta memorial champions and Dhakas Mohammedan Sporting. The Bangladesh team will kick off the meet against the Pradyut Dutta Memorial champions at the Salt Lake Stadium on February 25.       
	Announcing the fixture, IFA secretary Utpal Ganguly said on Friday that venues for semi-finals and the final would be decided later on since the Salt Lake Stadium will be unavailable for the Calcutta Book Fair. The semi-finals and final, on March 5 and 7 respectively, will be telecast live on ESPN.       
	FIXTURE       
	Feb. 25: Md. Sporting (Dhaka) vs P. Dutta champions (Salt Lake); Feb. 26: Mohun Bagan vs Churchill Brothers (Salt Lake); Feb. 27: Mahindra United vs Santos (Salt Lake); Feb. 28: Md. Sporting (Dhaka) vs Mohun Bagan (Salt Lake); Feb. 29: Churchill Brothers vs P. Dutta champions (Salt Lake); March 1: East Bengal vs Mahindra United (Barasat); March 2: Mohun Bagan vs P. Dutta champions (venue not decided); March 3: East Bengal vs Santos (venue not decided); March 4: Md. Sporting (Dhaka) vs Churchill Brothers (venue not decided); March 5: Semi final (venue not decided); March 7: Final (venue not decided).                 
	 The WBAWB-organised invitational mercantile basketball meet will be held at Rangers Club from Saturday to Friday. Ten mercantile companies are expected to take part.                 
	BASKETBALL: WBAWB-organised invitational mercantile meet at Rangers Club       
	RUGBY: All India Calcutta Cup finals  at SAI Eastern Region: Losers plate at 2pm and Main plate at 3.30pm.                                                                                                                                                                       
